    "where humans and GPT were instructed to response empathically to a human scenario, similar to the current study.",
    "The main dependent variable was participants' reports of feeling heard, and the effect size for the difference between human and AI was η2=0.046.",
    "Because the setup of the current study was very different from the Yin study, and to maximize power, we aimed to achieve a.99 power using the effect size from the Yin et al. paper.",
    "Our power analysis suggested that a sample of 382 participants would be required to achieve this level of power.",
    "We decided to collect data from 400 participants, assuming that some would be excluded due to failing the attention checks or providing non-sensical responses."
